members.name: ErrorEvent.message
members.description: Is a DOMString containing a human-readable error message describing the problem.

members.name: ErrorEvent.filename
members.description: Is a DOMString containing the name of the script file in which the error occurred.

members.name: ErrorEvent.lineno
members.description: Is an integer containing the line number of the script file on which the error occurred.

members.name: ErrorEvent.colno
members.description: Is an integer containing the column number of the script file on which the error occurred.

members.name: ErrorEvent.error
members.description: Is a JavaScript Object that is concerned by the event.

members.name: ErrorEvent()
members.description: Creates an ErrorEvent event with the given parameters.
